{
  "stem": "19807.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 83.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm in the store because one month, during the summer I would work in the store.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was only 10 years old, nine years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one month, I'll be going on vacation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They'll send me to a camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I could hear that my-- my-- my father's boss, who was childless, they didn't have any children, and I was very, very favorite of him-- he was supposed to bring me something from Germany, like a carry-on bag.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was explaining to my father, those are the night-- he witnessed the night that was the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's when the Germans went all over and broke all the windows in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, I couldn't wait to get on the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lucky that I got here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are in for bad times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then after the fascists came, and they established a law in defense of the nation, we had, from 10 years old, we had to wear the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because my-- my father's boss participated and he was awarded a medal during First World War, he wore only a yellow button.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He did not wear the star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was the privilege they accorded him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a shock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean it was just, just-- it came after-- first the restrictions came, then came the stars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First the restrictions came where all Jews could not walk on the main street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could not walk around the train station or the train stations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could not walk next to military areas, where in Plovdiv, they used to have-- they couldn't walk any place except certain designated areas and at certain hours.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they came, they came, the-- the-- the-- the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
